Thanks for looking.

"Demure"
48" Round
12 Layers
Hangs on a French Cleat
Took 1 Billion hours to design and make (Approximation)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fp9cDnd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I also find "Demure" extremely difficult to photograph.  Just the photo took me forever to get/edit. But, I'm happy with it.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lzak1QT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4mMJ7Vd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1ktuSBk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3YmLPy5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Thanks for looking.  If you want to see other things I make, check it out here:
philip-roberts.com/

