https://www.plancpills.org</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LFe70gX</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MilkMenace]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Somehow... Padmé returned</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/e8CXVje</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/R0n0DzP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/e8CXVje</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AlexSkullUterna]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Went to Planned Parenthood for the yearly</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/p740JtY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6qAVibr.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And man. I just cannot underscore how amazing it was. Got a mammogram scheduled, got an IUD inserted, got an appointment with a menopause doctor. Issues I’ve been discussing for years with my GP were addressed THEN. Like, at the appointment. Immediately. I had no idea IUD was an option for me. I had no idea there were doctors who focus on peri menopause & menopause. I WISH my regular doctor were even half as interested in my well being as this doctor was. 

AND There’s a literal Plan B vending machine outside. Chef’s kiss.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O3HOygA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I first went to PP when I was 15. They were my hero then, and 32 years later they still rock.  In closing: Got reproductive organs? Even old ones? Go to Planned Parenthood if it’s an option in your area. They bill insurance, give excellent care, & you get to support something important. #plannedparenthood #abortionishealthcare #fuckyouscotus</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/p740JtY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mbcb350]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I can breathe a little easier for two more years</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/W5EijBp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Q9tud8L.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I somehow forgot this was something he could do.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/W5EijBp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Chimaeraxxxxx]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Women</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/r7d6eGv</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OsXiiQ2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/r7d6eGv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DraMoonBreaker]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fetterman!!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/8BjQ1Af</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hkB6lD6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>#Fetterman</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/8BjQ1Af</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[codenametrixie]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And absolutely noone was surprised</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/suJDMKe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/janvyKZ.jpg" style="max-width: